## Phase 0: Pre-Development (Weeks -2 to 0)

### 0.1 Market Validation 🔴 P0

- [ ] **Interview 20-30 potential customers**

  - [ ] Identify 20-30 target companies (100-500 employees, manufacturing)
  - [ ] Schedule interviews (30 min each)
  - [ ] Prepare interview script (pain points, budget, current solutions)
  - [ ] Conduct interviews
  - [ ] Document findings (common pain points, willingness to pay, feature priorities)
  - [ ] Validate pricing model ($299-$799/month)
  - [ ] Identify 10+ companies interested in pilot program

- [ ] **Competitive research validation**

  - [ ] Sign up for Coupa trial/demo
  - [ ] Request SAP Ariba demo
  - [ ] Review Intelex demo
  - [ ] Document feature gaps and opportunities
  - [ ] Validate pricing positioning (50-70% cheaper)

- [ ] **Identify and secure 5 pilot customers** 🔴 P0
  - [ ] Shortlist 10 candidates from interviews
  - [ ] Present pilot program details (free access, 4-month commitment, feedback required)
  - [ ] Sign pilot agreements / LOIs (Letters of Intent)
  - [ ] Document pilot customer requirements
  - [ ] Schedule kickoff calls with each pilot

**Exit Criteria:** 5 pilot customers committed, market validation complete

